 ______________________________________
|                                      |
| init Menu:                           |
|                                      |
|       ======= ATM =======            |
|                                      |
|    [1]- Create a new account         |
|                                      |
|    [2]- Update account information   |
|                                      |
|    [3]- Check accounts               |
|                                      |
|    [4]- Check list of owned account  |
|                                      |
|    [5]- Make Transaction             |
|                                      |
|    [6]- Remove existing account      |
|                                      |
|    [7]- Transfer ownership           |
|                                      |
|    [8]- Exit                         |
|______________________________________|


